name: Experiment Or Die #99
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. I've been a punk, hard-core, metal kind of guy most of my life and when I met my wife I realized she liked a much cooler spectrum of music than I did including Hip-Hop. One of the things we did agree on though was our love for The Wu-Tang Clan. The first time I heard her jamming out to Wu-Tang I knew she was the one. Never again will such a wealth of talent be found in the same group. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
